                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Ask after every positive interaction. QR code on receipts works well for Guildford retail.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="15" data-category="reviews">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">All reviews responded to within 48 hours</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Respond to negative reviews professionally. Prospective clients read your responses.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="16" data-category="reviews">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">Review schema markup displaying star ratings</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">AggregateRating schema can show stars in search results, boosting CTR.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Citations & Links -->
    <div class="reveal" data-category="citations">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand">Citations & Links</h2>
        <span class="category-progress text-sm font-semibold text-text-muted" data-category-count="citations">0 / 4</span>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="17" data-category="citations">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">Listed in major UK directories (Yell, Thomson, FreeIndex)</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Consistency matters more than quantity. Ensure NAP matches GBP.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="18" data-category="citations">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">Listed in Guildford-specific directories</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Surrey Chamber of Commerce, Visit Guildford, Experience Guildford, local business associations.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="19" data-category="citations">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">Backlinks from local Guildford/Surrey sources</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Sponsor local events, partner with University of Surrey, contribute to Surrey Advertiser.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div class="checklist-item service-card !p-0 overflow-hidden" data-id="20" data-category="citations">
          <label class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 cursor-pointer select-none">
            <input type="checkbox" class="checklist-checkbox mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-border accent-accent shrink-0" />
            <div class="flex-1">
              <span class="checklist-label font-semibold text-brand">Google Search Console and Bing Webmaster Tools set up</span>
              <details class="mt-2">
                <summary class="text-sm text-accent font-medium cursor-pointer hover:underline">View tip</summary>
                <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mt-1.5 leading-relaxed">Essential for monitoring indexation, clicks, and identifying technical issues.</p>
              </details>
            </div>
          </label>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Local SEO Matters in Guildford -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 reveal">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand mb-5">Why Local SEO Matters in Guildford</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-brand max-w-none text-text-muted leading-relaxed space-y-4">
      <p>Guildford is one of the most commercially competitive towns in the South East. Average commercial rents on the High Street sit among the highest outside London, and property prices across the GU1-GU4 postcodes mean that every business carries significant fixed costs. Winning organic local traffic is not a luxury &mdash; it is the difference between thriving and subsidising rent with paid ads indefinitely.</p>
      <p>The local search landscape breaks into three battlegrounds. First, the Google local pack: the three-listing map result that captures over 40% of clicks for service queries. Second, organic results beneath the pack, where location-specific content and technical health determine who appears. Third, the emerging AI search layer &mdash; Copilot, Gemini, and ChatGPT &mdash; where structured data and entity authority decide which businesses get cited.</p>
